1.00	Kirkton_of_Tough	Kirkton of Tough	Kirkton of Tough is a settlement in the Marr area of Aberdeenshire, Scotland at grid reference . It is about 4 kilometres (2.5 mi) southeast of Alford and 143 kilometres (89 mi) from Edinburgh. Tough is where the world famous, aberdeen angus breed of cattle was first bred.	
